          <p>When you submit information to ASW, it is collected, processed and maintained solely by us or by our third party contractors, in particular in the European Union, Brazil, India and the United States of America, those third party contractors being bound by our privacy policy or by restrictions at least as restrictive as those set forth in this policy. Your information may be disclosed to third parties in those countries to facilitate the printing and shipping of your ASW Membership Card.</p>
          <p>Partners may sponsor special member offers, promotions, privileges or contests that require you to disclose personal information. We will never disclose private member data, including email addresses, to partners without your prior express consent. Certain partners may require members to opt-in or agree to terms on the partners’ landing pages authorizing us to provide their information to the partner in question. We advise you always to check our partners’ privacy policies before submitting information about yourself.</p>
