            <li class="asw-mb--m">to identify, contact or bring legal action against you if you are violating our Terms of Service or other rules or if we believe you are causing injury or interference with the rights of members, the general public or ASW;</li>
            <li class="asw-mb--m">if we or substantially all of our assets are acquired by a third party, in which case personal information held by us will be some of the transferred assets; and</li>
            <li class="asw-mb--m">if we are under a duty to disclose or share your personal information in order to comply with any legal obligation, or in order to enforce or apply our Terms of Service and other agreements or to protect our rights, property, or safety of our customers, or others.</li>
